name: viewASupplier

testSteps.description: Given that I'm logged in to 'Supplier Creation' page

children.description: When i open page from sidebar menu: {Supplier Management,Supplier Creation}

testSteps.description: Then the 'Supplier Management' page and its contents should show up
When I set the Supplier to '54556'
When i click on search button
Then a search result should show up containing the supplier name 'TEST SUPPLIER EDITED'
When i click on bank accounts button of the first supplier
Then the supplier bank accounts modal and its contents should show up
When i close modal
When i click on view button of the first supplier
Then the 'Supplier Address Book Creation' form should show up
Then the 'Supplier Name' accordion form should open
Then the Alpha Name field shoud be set to 'TEST SUPPLIER EDITED'
When i expand the mailing list accordion form
Then the 'Mailing List' accordion form should open
When i expand the contact information accordion form
Then the 'Contact Information' accordion form should open
When i click on supplier master creation header button
Then the 'Supplier Master Creation' form should show up
Then the 'Internal Information Part 1' accordion form should open
When i expand the internal information part two accordion form
When i click on exit button
Then the 'Supplier Management' page and its contents should show up

title: View a supplier
